      • index

        private int index
        The internally-stored index. This value is updated during iteration. Otherwise, it's practically invalid and should be ignored.

      • exceptionConsumer

        private static final java.util.function.Consumer<java.lang.Exception> exceptionConsumer
        An internal consumer for exceptions. Exceptions that have nowhere else to go will be caught and passed to this consumer.
